<br>
I wish people realize that you can only sell 30 items at a time.  E.G. People having 4 or more satchels. Items are not moving that Fast!<br>
<br>
I wish people realize to organize item better.<br>
E.G. Put better items on 1st 3 satchels or more sellable items.<br>
<br>
I wish everyone stop lumping together in same spots.  All near the bank, there are so many area that is not so dense or empty.  E.G. Closer to Arena and it less lag.<br>
<br>
I wish people read zone in or login message.  It tells you /bazaar and /Trader.  Stop asking! Especially Over and Over.<br>
<br>
I wish people realize Bazaar is competitive.  No one going to buy Item at inflated prices when 2 plus others are selling at a lot lower price. Especially if items are not selling.  Sheez.  3k for Ice Coment, Xegony(Note: if you want to look, it still there).<br>
<br>
Lastly, I wish people stop congesting the Aisles, especially by the bank.  Either move close to the bank or the wall.  Especially stop blocking nexus or Shadowhaven zone.  There is so much space to stand there and /bazaar or talk.  Suggestion: Use the Arena Area, less Lag.<br>
